@startuml m7-pdb-quorum-coupling-activity
skinparam dpi 300
title M7 — Quorum-Aware Voluntary Disruption

start
:cluster change / drain requested;
:compute quorum need + handoff capacity;
:set PDB minAvailable / maxUnavailable;
if (eviction respects PDB? quorum safe?) then (yes)
  #ccffcc:allow eviction -> handoff -> proceed;
  stop
else (no)
  #ccffcc:block eviction (protect quorum);
  stop
endif
legend right
  Voluntary disruptions (drains, rolling
  updates) never break :global/Horde quorum
  or exceed handoff throughput.
endlegend
@enduml
